Hello <@U049N17LXQC> if you want to reduce your tbt.You have to review a lot of things:
• Reduce image size and use webp format for images
• Use lazy loading for loading images
• Manage broken links or 404 error by redirects
• Use less library in the code
• Use preload for css and javascript
Here are some extensions that will help you better manage this
*Broken link CHECKER*
*Meta SEO Inspector*
*Image size info: extension*
*Pagespeed Insights*
